<summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a>的onafterprint属性是用于处理当前窗口的<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">afterprint (en-US)</a></code>事件的<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code>。这些事件会在被用户打印结束或者中止打印窗口的情况下触发。</p>\n\n<p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeprint (en-US)</a></code>和<code>afterprint</code>&nbsp;事件允许页面在打印开始前修改它们的内容（比如移除一个横幅等），打印结束后，这些修改会恢复原状。一般情况下，你更喜欢使用&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries#Media_types\">@media print</a></code>&nbsp;CSS规则，但是在某些情况下这些事件会有他们的必要性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>window</em>.addEventListener(\"afterprint\", function(event) { ... });\n<em>window</em>.onafterprint = <em>event handling code</em>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"提示","title":"提示","isH3":false,"content":"<p>某些浏览器（包括 Firefox 6 及更高版本和 Internet Explorer）用触发<code>beforeprint</code> 和<code>afterprint</code>的方式来确定何时进行了打印。你可以在打印期间用这个方式来调整用户界面（UI）的表现（比如在打印过程中展示或隐藏一些界面元素）。</p>\n\n<p><code>afterprint</code>会在用户打印完成或取消打印会话后触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification 规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status 状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment 备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage//multipage/webappapis.html#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">onafterprint</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多请见","title":"更多请见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/print\"><code>window.print</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\"><code>window.onbeforeprint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/Printing\" title=\"Printing\">Printing</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"grammarly-disable-indicator\" id=\"sect2\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"提示","id":"提示"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"更多请见","id":"更多请见"}],"summary":"WindowEventHandlers的onafterprint属性是用于处理当前窗口的afterprint (en-US)事件的event handler。这些事件会在被用户打印结束或者中止打印窗口的情况下触发。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/window/afterprint_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/window/afterprint_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window","title":"window.minimize"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event","title":"WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint"}],"pageTitle":"WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint | MDN","noIndexing":true}}